This turn, each time you gain a card, set it aside, and put it into your hand at end of turn.

name: Foray
description: Discard 3 cards, revealing them. If they have 3 different names, gain a Loot.

name: Launch
description:
Once per turn: Return to your Action phase.
'''+1 Card''', '''+1 Action''', and '''+1 Buy'''.

name: Scrounge
description:
Choose one: Trash a card from your hand;
or gain an Estate from the trash, and if you did, gain a card costing up to {{Cost|5}}.

name: Looting
description: Gain a Loot.

name: Invasion
description:
You may play an Attack from your hand.
Gain a Duchy. Gain an Action onto your deck.
Gain a Loot; play it.

name: Cage
description: Set aside up to 4 cards from your hand face down (on this). The next time you gain a Victory card, trash this, and put the set aside cards into your hand at end of turn.

name: Grotto
description:
'''+1 Action'''
Set aside up to 4 cards from your hand face down (on this). At the start of your next turn, discard them, then draw as many.

name: Search
description:
+{{Cost|2}}
The next time a Supply pile empties, trash this and gain a Loot.

name: Cabin Boy
description:
'''+1 Card
+1 Action'''
At the start of your next turn, choose one: +{{Cost|2}}; or trash this to gain a Duration card.

name: Crucible
description:
Trash a card from your hand.
+{{Cost|1}} per {{Cost|1}} it costs.

name: Fortune Hunter
description:
+{{Cost|2}}
Look at the top 3 cards of your deck. You may play a Treasure from them. Put the rest back in any order.

name: Gondola
description: Either now or at the start of your next turn: +{{Cost|2}}.{{divline}}When you gain this, you may play an Action card from your hand.

name: Harbor Village
description:
'''+1 Card
+2 Actions'''
After the next Action you play this turn, if it gave you +{{Cost}}, +{{Cost|1}}.

name: Mapmaker
description: Look at the top 4 cards of your deck. Put 2 into your hand and discard the rest.{{divline}}When any player gains a Victory card, you may play this from your hand.

name: Maroon
description: Trash a card from your hand. '''+2 Cards''' per type it has (Action, Attack, etc.).

name: Crew
description:
'''+3 Cards'''
At the start of your next turn, put this onto your deck.

name: Enlarge
description: Now and at the start of your next turn: Trash a card from your hand, and gain one costing up to {{Cost|2}} more.

name: Cutthroat
description:
Each other player discards down to 3 cards in hand.

The next time anyone gains a Treasure costing {{Cost|5}} or more, gain a Loot.

name: Figurine
description:
'''+2 Cards'''
You may discard an Action card for {{nowrap|'''+1 Buy'''}} and +{{Cost|1}}.

name: Frigate
description:
+{{Cost|3}}
Until the start of your next turn, each time another player plays an Action card, they discard down to 4 cards in hand afterwards.

name: Longship
description:
'''+2 Actions'''
At the start of your next turn, '''+2 Cards'''.

name: Pilgrim
description:
'''+4 Cards'''
Put a card from your hand onto your deck.

name: Quartermaster
description: At the start of each of your turns for the rest of the game, choose one: Gain a card costing up to {{Cost|4}}, setting it aside on this; or put a card from this into your hand.

name: Silver Mine
description: Gain a Treasure costing less than this to your hand.

name: Trickster
description:
Each other player gains a Curse.
Once this turn, when you discard a Treasure from play, you may set it aside. Put it in your hand at end of turn.
